-- Fresh 4-player blackjack table
-- Secure account version with chunked cipher packets:
--   - Uses advanced_cipher_2
--   - Gets account public key from account computer
--   - Creates local blackjack reply keypair
--   - Sends encrypted/chunked account requests
--   - Decrypts encrypted/chunked account replies
