-- IMPORTANT:
--   The account computer must also support chunked secure packets:
--     packet.chunked = true
--     packet.payloadChunks = { encryptedPiece1, encryptedPiece2, ... }
--   Otherwise blackjack can encrypt safely but the account computer will not understand it.

